; Test commodity directive with sub-directives (line 534 of textual_directives.cc)
; Exercise commodity format, nomarket, note, default, and alias sub-directives

commodity EUR
    format 1.000,00 EUR
    nomarket
    note European currency
    alias EU

2024/01/01 Test
    Expenses:Food    10,00 EUR
    Assets:Cash

test bal
          -10,00 EUR  Assets:Cash
           10,00 EUR  Expenses:Food
--------------------
                   0
end test
